<h3 data-path-to-node="8">🎮 About My Project</h3>
<p data-path-to-node="9">This is a small game of throwing a snowball, competing against a computer opponent.</p>
<p data-path-to-node="9">User uses the left and right arrows to aim, and the up and down arrows to control the power of their throw.</p>
